Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.80,0:01:30.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我就是你的过去"  她说  "就你"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I thought I was your past." She said, "You?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:32.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说  "好吧  我们毕竟相处很久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said, "Well, we go back a long way.
