Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:56.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,我让她坐在战争纪念碑旁那个她常坐的位子上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd parked her by the war memorial in her usual seat while I went
