Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.31,0:26:31.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,你可以把那两件衬衫熨了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"You could iron those two shirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.44,0:26:34.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,吃一片药  给我们一个吻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Take a tablet. Give us a kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.35,0:26:35.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Toodle-pip."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.40,0:26:42.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,我走进里屋  在那里他们看不见我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I went into the back room... where they couldn't see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.96,0:26:49.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,我拉上窗帘  坐在黑暗中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I draw the curtains, and I'm sitting there in the dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.00,0:26:53.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,直到我好像听到了敲门声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..when I think I hear a knock at the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.64,0:26:55.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我一动不动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.48,0:26:59.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,又一阵更大的敲门声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}..and there's another knock, louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.16,0:27:04.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,我像乔杜里医生说的那样  告诉自己这不是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do like Dr Chaudhury says and tell myself it's not happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.07,0:27:05.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,可惜事与愿违\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}only it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.83,0:27:09.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,有人透过信箱大喊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Somebody shouts through the letterbox,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.55,0:27:10.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,"我知道你在里面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I know you're in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.72,0:27:12.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,开门"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Open this door."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.96,0:27:15.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就去开门了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.52,0:27:18.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,有个人在门外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And there is someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.72,0:27:21.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,是个女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.55,0:27:25.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说  "你是那个儿子吗"  我说  "什么"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She said, "Are you the son?" I said, "What?"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.80,0:27:28.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说  "你是那个儿子吗  我是那个女儿"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She said, "Are you the son? I'm the daughter."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.55,0:27:31.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说  "是你一直在监视这个房子吗"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said, "Have you been watching the house?"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.16,0:27:33.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说  "偶尔吧  怎么了"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She said, "On and off. Why?"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.76,0:27:36.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说  "没什么"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said, "Uh... Nothing."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.16,0:27:40.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说  "我不知道穿什么看起来更合适"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She said, "I don't know what there is to look so suited about."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.87,0:27:44.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说  "你还是进来说话吧"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said, "You'd better come in."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.68,0:28:09.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,当我听到外面汽车的声音时已经是九点钟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's nine o'clock when I hear the car outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.83,0:28:12.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,我正坐着看电视\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sitting watching TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.40,0:28:14.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说  你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said, "Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.52,0:28:17.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,"玩得开心吗"  她说  "开心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Did you have a good time?" She said, "Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.72,0:28:19.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我们很开心  谢谢"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Yes, we did, thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.96,0:28:22.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说  "买到你要的防晒霜了吗"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said, "Did you get your sun tan lotion?"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.72,0:28:24.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说  "什么防晒霜"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She said, "What sun tan lotion?"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.44,0:28:27.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,"你不是要去买防晒霜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"You were going to get some sun tan lotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.48,0:28:29.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,算了不重要  你已经忘了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Doesn't matter. You've forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.92,0:28:31.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,特恩布尔先生怎么样"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"How's Mr Turnbull?"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.83,0:28:34.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,"弗兰克吗  他很好"  她脱下了衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Frank? He's all right." She took her things off.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.72,0:28:37.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说  "格雷厄姆  我相信你会喜欢上他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She said, "I'm sure you could get to like him, Graham,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.92,0:28:39.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,只要你慢慢了解他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"if only you got to know him."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.40,0:28:42.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说  好吧  那你应该带他进来"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said, "Well, you should have brought him in."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.20,0:28:44.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,"下次我会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Well, I will next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.83,0:28:49.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们三个能时不时一起出门就太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"It'd be nice if now and again we could go off as a threesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.68,0:28:50.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,你都干了些什么"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"What have you done?"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.20,0:28:53.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说  "什么也没干  就坐在这里"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Nothing," I said. "Just sat here."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.52,0:28:55.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,"你没有不高兴吗"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"And you've been all right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.68,0:28:59.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,"你知道的"  她说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"You see," she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.92,0:29:03.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,"外面一个人也没有"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"There wasn't anybody outside."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.28,0:29:05.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,"不是  外面有人"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Oh, yes, there was."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.72,0:29:09.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,"格雷厄姆  你吃药了吗  吃一片药"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Oh, Graham. Have you had a tablet? Have a tablet."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.24,0:29:11.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,"我不想吃药\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I don't want a tablet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.96,0:29:14.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你外面有谁来过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I'll tell you who was outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.72,0:29:17.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,帕梅拉·马斯格雷夫女士"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Mrs Pamela Musgrave."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.24,0:29:18.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说  "那是谁"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She said, "Who's that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.72,0:29:21.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,"娘家姓特恩布尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Nee Turnbull.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.28,0:29:23.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,你未婚夫的女儿"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"The daughter of your hubby-to-be."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.80,0:29:26.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说  "他没有女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She said, "He hasn't got a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.16,0:29:28.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,他有一个儿子在南方  他没有女儿"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"He's got a son down south. He hasn't got a daughter."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.16,0:29:31.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说  "你现在开始说胡话了  快吃药"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She said, "You're just making stuff up now. Have a tablet."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.64,0:29:33.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说  "我没有胡说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said, "I'm not making it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.80,0:29:36.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有其他事情我也没有胡说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"And there's something else I'm not making up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.76,0:29:39.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,特恩布尔夫人"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Mrs Turnbull."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.96,0:29:43.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说  "没有什么特恩布尔夫人  她已经死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She said, "There isn't a Mrs Turnbull. She's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.40,0:29:45.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要去厕所了"  我说  "她没死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I'm going to the lav." I said, "She's not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.72,0:29:47.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,她正心碎地坐在轮椅上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"She's in a wheelchair with a broken heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.31,0:29:48.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,他一直在骗你"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"He's been having you on."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.64,0:29:53.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,过了一会  她从厕所出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After a bit she comes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.83,0:29:55.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,"你不过是空口无凭罢了"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"You're just saying all this."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.28,0:29:59.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,"便笺簿上有个号码  打过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"There's a number on the pad. Ring up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.48,0:30:02.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,是他的妻子  身有残疾已经十年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"She's disabled, is his wife. Has been for ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.35,0:30:04.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们的女儿在照顾父母\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Their daughter looks after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.87,0:30:07.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,你并不是第一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"You're not the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.80,0:30:08.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,他经常这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"He's always doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.00,0:30:11.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,有个女人  本来要和他去巴巴多斯岛的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"One woman, it was going to be Barbados.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.76,0:30:14.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,有人在博尔顿修道院发现你们在一起就告诉了他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Somebody spotted you together at Bolton Abbey.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.59,0:30:15.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,真心祝福你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"A well-wisher.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.20,0:30:19.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,特内里费岛"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Tenerife!"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.64,0:30:25.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,过了一会  我给她端了一杯茶  她一直在哭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Later on, I took her a cup of tea. She'd been crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.07,0:30:28.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说  "我买了这件小睡衣"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She said, "I bought this little bed jacket."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.35,0:30:31.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说  "对不起  妈"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said, "I'm sorry, Mam."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.40,0:30:34.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说  "他一点没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She said, "He was right enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.92,0:30:37.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,在我这个年纪还想要什么  我年纪多大了"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"What can you expect at my age? How old am I?"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.40,0:30:40.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说  "你72岁了"  她说  "还有一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I said, you're 72." She said, "That's another thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.87,0:30:44.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,我和他一起回记得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"..I remembered with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.52,0:30:47.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,和你一起就会不记得"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I don't remember with you."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.07,0:30:49.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说  "对不起"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said, "I'm sorry."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.24,0:30:51.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说  "你没有对不起  你有什么好对不起的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She said, "You're not sorry. "How are you sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.04,0:30:52.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,你本来就不喜欢他"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"You didn't like him."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.83,0:30:54.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说  "他配不上你"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said, "He wasn't good enough for you."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.16,0:30:56.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说  "配不配的我最清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She said, "I'm the best judge of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.44,0:30:58.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,他潇洒帅气  比你强多了"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"He was natty. More than can be said for you."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.04,0:31:00.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,又开始哭了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Starts crying again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.07,0:31:07.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说  "我理解你  妈"  她说  "你不理解"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said, "I understand, Mam." She said, "You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.24,0:31:10.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,"你怎么会理解  你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"How can you understand? You...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.83,0:31:13.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不是个正常人"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"..you're not normal"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.35,0:31:16.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说  "我去睡觉了"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said, "I'm going to bed."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.92,0:31:21.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,过了一会  她在门外喊道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a bit she comes shouting outside the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.35,0:31:23.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,"你以为你比我厉害  格雷厄姆·惠特克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"You think you've got it over me, Graham Whittaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.24,0:31:25.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,但你并没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Well...you haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.68,0:31:28.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,是我赢了你"  我说  "去睡觉吧"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I've got it over you." I said, "Go to bed."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.16,0:31:31.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说  "我知道你看的杂志都是些什么东西"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She said, "I know the kind of magazines you read."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.11,0:31:33.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说  "国际象棋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said, "Chess.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.83,0:31:36.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,你会感冒的"  她说  "根本不是国际象棋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"You'll catch cold." She said, "They never are chess.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.48,0:31:38.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,不穿衣服的国际象棋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Chess with no clothes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.00,0:31:41.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,一丝不挂的象棋  那种象棋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Chess in their birthday suits. That kind of chess.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.07,0:31:42.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,象棋男"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Chess men."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.83,0:31:44.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说  "回去睡觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I say, "Go back to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.00,0:31:47.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,关上你的电热毯"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Turn your blanket off."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.24,0:31:53.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,转天  她完全好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Next day, she's right as rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.55,0:31:55.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,她已经忘了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's forgotten it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.44,0:31:58.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,反正是不再提了  除了我们要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never mentions it, anyway, except just as we're
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.24,0:32:02.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,出门的时候她说  "格雷厄姆  我真的爱你"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}leaving the house she says, "I do love you, Graham."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.59,0:32:05.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说  "我也爱你"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said, "I love you, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.48,0:32:10.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说  不管怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She said, "Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.48,0:32:13.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,"他要戴助听器"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"..he had a hearing aid."
